Module hanyaeger.api
Package com.github.hanyaeger.api.engine.entities.entity.motion

Interface Newtonian

All Superinterfaces:
Anchorable, Bounded, BufferedMovable, DimensionsProvider, DirectionProvider, GameNode, MotionModifier, Movable, NewtonianModifier, Placeable, SpeedProvider
public interface Newtonian
extends BufferedMovable, NewtonianModifier
A Newtonian is a special case of a Movable that abides the basic laws of gravity and friction. It should be used for Dynamic Entities that should also display some physics behaviour. This physics is rather elemental and should not be compared for fully fledged physics.
